does the nm patch work?
does this have an expiration date ? can i keep it? or after the final release comes out, its not going to work ?

1. copy to Commend file to desktop (drag icon)
2. run terminal (Applications -> Utilities -> Terminal)
3. change to desktop folder ('cd Desktop')
4. make sure permissions are set on nm command ('chmod 755 nm')
5. run patch ('./MS\ Office\ 2011\ Mac\ Patch.command')
6. Run office and enter serials provided in the other torrent ;)
